 2019 |website=Leeds United Official Site |access-date=3 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n=== Other senior players under contract ===\n{{updated|30 January 2020}} \n<!-- to be sorted by 1 Role, 2 Name -->\n{{Fs start}}\n{{fs player | no= | nat=NED | pos=MF | name=[[Ouasim Bouy]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player | no= | nat=BEL | pos=DF | name=[[Laurens De Bock]]|other=on loan to [[ADO Den Haag]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{fs player | no= | nat=EIR | pos=DF | name=[[Conor Shaughnessy]]|other=on loan to [[Burton Albion]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player | no= | nat=SPA | pos=FW | name=Adri\u00e1n Balboa|other=on loan to [[Lorca FC]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{Fs player | no= | nat=NED | pos=FW | name=[[Jay-Roy Grot]]|other=on loan to [[SBV Vitesse|Vitesse]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player | no= | nat=ESP | pos=FW | name=[[Rafa M\u00fajica]]|other=on loan to [[Villarreal CF B]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player | no= | nat=BUL | pos=FW | name=[[Kun Temenuzhkov]]|other=on loan to [[CF La Nuc\u00eda|La Nuc\u00eda]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Reserves and academy===\n{{main|Leeds United F.C. Reserves and Youth Team}}\n\n===Retired numbers===\n{{main|Retired numbers in association football}}\nOn 15 May 2014, Leeds United retired the number 17 shirt due to then-owner [[Massimo Cellino]]'s superstitious beliefs. Up until June 2014, the last occupant of the shirt had been [[Michael Brown (footballer, born 1977)|Michael Brown]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.itv.com/news/calendar/2014-05-15/not-for-tv-cellinos-best-bits/ |title=Massimo Cellino says Leeds \"has no manager\" |date=15 May 2014 |work=ITV |access-date=15 May 2014}}</ref> The shirt was brought out of retirement on 3 July 2019, when Leeds new signing of [[Portugal national football team|Portugal]] international [[H\u00e9lder Costa (footballer)|H\u00e9lder Costa]] was given the number.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/team-news/25119/leeds-united-complete-h