ldailymail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/hull-citys-backroom-team-undergoes-1717175 |title=Hull City's backroom team undergoes summer overhaul ahead of the new season |last=Philip Buckingham |date=26 June 2018 |website=Hull Live |publisher=Hull Daily Mail |access-date=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Fitness Coach|| {{flagicon|SPA}} Rub\u00e9n Crespo<ref name=summeroverhauljune2018/>\n|-\n|Fitness Coach|| {{flagicon|FRA}} Benoit Delaval<ref name=firstteamstaff/>\n|-\n|Sports Scientist||{{flagicon|ENG}} Tom Robinson<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/team-news/20941/united-enter-catapult-partnership |title=United Enter Catapult Partnership |date=29 June 2016 |website=Leeds United F.C. |access-date=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Sports Scientist||{{flagicon|GRE}} Alexandros Kapsis<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/education/24852/leeds-united-link-up-with-leeds-beckett-university |title=LEEDS UNITED LINK-UP WITH LEEDS BECKETT UNIVERSITY |date=23 April 2019 |website=Leeds United |access-date=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|Head Physio||{{flagicon|IRE}} [[Henry McStay]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/football/leeds-united/leeds-united-physio-price-seems-right-man-for-new-boss-bielsa-1-9280447 |title=Leeds United: Physio' Price seems right man for new boss Bielsa |last=Phil Hay |date=2 August 2018 |website=Yorkshire Evening Post |access-date=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Assistant Physio||{{flagicon|ENG}} Daryl Carter<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club/23904/leeds-beckett-partnership-continues-to-grow |title=LEEDS BECKETT PARTNERSHIP CONTINUES TO GROW |date=24 September 2018 |website=Leeds United = |access-date=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|Assistant Physio||{{flagicon|ENG}} William Atton<ref>https://www.yorkshiresportsmedicine.co.uk/meet-the-team/</ref>\n|-\n|Head Of Nutrition||{{flagicon|ENG}} Nessan Costello<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsbeckett.ac.uk/blogs/carnegie-xchange/2