-bielsa-1-9280447 |title=Leeds United: Physio' Price seems right man for new boss Bielsa |last=Phil Hay |date=2 August 2018 |website=Yorkshire Evening Post |access-date=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Assistant Physio||{{flagicon|ENG}} Daryl Carter<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club/23904/leeds-beckett-partnership-continues-to-grow |title=LEEDS BECKETT PARTNERSHIP CONTINUES TO GROW |date=24 September 2018 |website=Leeds United = |access-date=13 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|Assistant Physio||{{flagicon|ENG}} William Atton<ref>https://www.yorkshiresportsmedicine.co.uk/meet-the-team/</ref>\n|-\n|Head Of Nutrition||{{flagicon|ENG}} Nessan Costello<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsbeckett.ac.uk/blogs/carnegie-xchange/2019/02/leeds-united-performance-nutrition--leeds-beckett-university/ |title=Leeds United Performance Nutrition & Leeds Beckett University |date=22 February 2019 |website=Leeds Beckett University |access-date=2 June 2019}}</ref>\n{{Fb oi footer|u=18 June 2018 |s=Leeds United and Yorkshire Evening Post|date=June 2018}}\n\n==Scouting team==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Position\n!Staff\n|-\n|Head of European Recruitment||{{flagicon|SPA}} Gaby Ruiz<ref name=\"scouting\">{{cite news |url=https://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/football/leeds-united/phil-hay-leeds-united-s-scouting-network-is-paying-dividends-1-8751738 |title=Phil Hay: Leeds United's scouting network is paying dividends |last=Phil Hay |newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post |access-date=18 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Head of Football Development (Asia)||{{flagicon|Japan}} [[Toshiya Fujita]]<ref name=scouting/>\n|-\n|Head of Emerging Talent||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Craig Dean (footballer)|Craig Dean]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/sport/football/leeds-united/leeds-united-net-oxford-scout-as-diagouraga-joins-pilgrims-1-8795744 |title=Leeds United net Oxford scout as Diagouraga joins Pilgrims |last=Phil Hay |date=9 October 2017 |newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post |access-date=18 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|Scout||{{flagicon|SPA}} [[Dani Salas]]<ref name=scouting/>\n|-\n|Scout||{{flagicon|SPA}} Paco Peral<ref name=scouting/>\n|-\n|Recruitment Analyst||{{flagicon|ENG}} Alex Davies<ref name=scouting/>\n|-\n|Recruitment Analyst||{{flagicon|FRA}} Andrea Iore<ref name=scouting/>\n{{Fb oi footer|u=15 May 2018 |s=Yorkshire Evening Post|date=June 2018}}\n\n===Under 23s and Academy staff===\n{{Main|Leeds United F.C. Reserves and Youth Team}}\n\n==Directors and backroom staff==\n\n===Owners and directors===\n[[File:Andrea Radrizzani profile GroupCEO MPSilva.png|180px|right|thumb|[[Andrea Radrizzani]] Leeds United's current 'majority' Owner]]\nSource:<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/club/Ownership-structure |title=Ownership structure \u2013 Leeds United |website=www.leedsunited.com |access-date=15 March 2018}}</ref>\n{{fb oi header}}\n{{fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Leeds United Football Club Limited ('LUFC') Owners |s={{flagicon|Italy}} Aser Group Holding (90% shares)}}\n{{fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Leeds United Football Club Limited ('LUFC') Owners |s={{flagicon|USA}} [[Denise DeBartolo York|49ers Enterprises]] (10% shares)}}\n{{fb cs staff |bg= |p=Honorary President |s={{flagicon|England}} [[David Lascelles, 8th Earl of Harewood]]}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club-news/24480/earl-of-harewood-named-honorary-president |title=EARL OF HAREWOOD NAMED HONORARY PRESIDENT |date=1 February 2019 |website=www.leedsunited.com |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602111951/https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club-news/24480/earl-of-harewood-named-honorary-president |archive-date=2 June 2019 |access-date=2 June 2019}}</ref>\n{{fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Chairman / Owner |s={{flagicon|Italy}} [[Andrea Radrizzani]] }} \n{{fb cs staff |bg= |p=Chief Executive|s={{flagicon|England}} Angus Kinnear }}\n \n{{fb cs staff |bg= |p=Director |s={{flagicon|USA}} Paraag Marathe}} \n{{fb cs staff |bg= |p=Director |s={{flagicon|Italy}} Andre Tegner }} \n{{fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Director of Football|s={{flagicon|Spain}} Victor Orta}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club-news/21945/director-of-football-appointed |title=Director of Football Appointed |website=www.leedsunited.com |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926114434/https://www.leedsunited.com/news/club-news/21945/director-of-football-appointed |archive-date=26 September 2018 |access-date=19 January 2018}}</ref>\n{{fb cs staff |bg= |p=Executive Director |s={{flagicon|England}} Paul Bell}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leedsunited.com/news/team-news/395/united-appoint-new-executive-director |title=United Appoint New Executive Director |website=www.leedsunited.com |access-date=19 January 2018}}</ref>\n{{Fb oi footer|u=1 May 2018 |s=Leeds United Official Website |date=May 2018}}\n\n==League history==\n{|\n|-\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*1920\u20131924: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1924\u20131927: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n*1927\u20131928: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1928\u20131931: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n*1931\u20131932: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1932\u20131947: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n*1947\u20131956: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1956\u20131960: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n|width=\"50\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*1960\u20131964: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1964\u20131982: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n*1982\u20131990: [[Football League Second Division|Division 2]]\n*1990\u20131992: [[Football League First Division|Division 1]]\n*1992\u20132004: [[Premier League]]\n*2004\u20132007: [[Football League Championship|Championship]]\n*2007\u20132010: [[Football League One|League One]]\n*2010&nbsp;\u2013 present: [[Football League Championship|Championship]]\n|}\n\n== Manager/Head Coach history